## Error Code Patterns Summary

### Regular Orders (Lotte-integrated)

| Error Source | Code Pattern | Example | Has `message` field? |
|--------------|--------------|---------|---------------------|
| TradeX Validation | `INVALID_PARAMETER` | Missing required field | ❌ NO |
| TradeX Auth | `UNAUTHORIZED`, `TOKEN_EXPIRED` | Invalid JWT | ✅ YES |
| Lotte Business | `{OPERATION}_{LOTTE_CODE}` | `ORDER_PLACE_1005` | ✅ YES (from Lotte) |

### TradeX-Native Orders (TP/SL, Stop, etc.)

| Error Source | Code Pattern | Example | Has `message` field? |
|--------------|--------------|---------|---------------------|
| TradeX Validation | `INVALID_PARAMETER` | Missing required field | ❌ NO |
| TradeX Auth | `UNAUTHORIZED`, `TOKEN_EXPIRED` | Invalid JWT | ✅ YES |
| TradeX Business | `{DESCRIPTIVE_NAME}` | `TP_PRICE_MUST_BE_HIGHER_THAN_ENTRY` | ❌ NO |

