## Quick Reference Table

| Feature | Regular Orders | TP/SL Orders |
|---------|---------------|--------------|
| **Success Response** | `{ message, orderNumber }` | `{ id }` |
| **Has `message` in success?** | ✅ YES (from Lotte) | ❌ NO |
| **Message includes `[CODE]`?** | ✅ YES | N/A |
| **Error code pattern** | `{OP}_{LOTTE_CODE}` | `{DESCRIPTIVE_NAME}` |
| **Has `message` in error?** | ✅ YES (from Lotte) | ❌ NO |
| **Uses `messageParams`?** | ❌ NO (Lotte provides message) | ✅ YES |
| **Query response** | N/A (use Lotte APIs) | Rich data array |
| **Language handling** | Via Lotte `lang_code` | Via TradeX i18n |

