## Usage Instructions

1. **Creating new Order API spec:**
   - Read this rule FIRST
   - Determine integration type (Lotte vs TradeX-native)
   - Follow corresponding pattern EXACTLY
   - Reference existing implementations

2. **Reviewing Order API spec:**
   - Check response format matches pattern
   - Verify error codes follow convention
   - Ensure NO mixing of patterns
   - Validate checklist items

3. **Explaining to stakeholders:**
   - Show comparison table
   - Explain rationale (bandwidth, consistency, FE needs)
   - Reference existing Stop Order implementation as proof

